<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَسَبْعُونَ أَلْفًا مِنْ مَلائِكَةِ الرِّضَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تُصَلِّي عَلَى مَنْ عَادَ مُمْسًى إِلَى الْغَدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِنْ عَادَهُ فِي أَوَّلَ الْيَوْمِ وَاصَلَتْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَلَيْهِ إِلَى اللَّيْلِ الصَّلاةَ فَاسْنِدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَمِنْهُمْ مُغِبًّا عُدْ وَخَفِّفْ وَمِنْهُمْ الَّذِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لَذِي يُؤَثِّرُ التَّطْوِيلَ مِنْ مُتَوَدِّدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَفَكِّرْ وَرَاعِ فِي الْعِيَادَةِ حَالَ مَنْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَعُودُ وَلا تُكْثِرْ سُؤَالاً تُنَكِّدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَذَكِّرُ لِمَنْ تَأْتِي وَقَوِّ فُؤَادِهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَمُرْهُ بِأَنْ يُوصِي إِذَا خِفْتَ وَارْشُدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَنَدِّ بِمَاءٍ أَوْ شَرَابٍ لِسَانَهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَقِّنْهُ عِنْدَ الْمَوْتِ قَوْلَ الْمُوَحَّدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَلا تُضْجِرَنْ بَلْ إِنْ تَكَلَّمَ بَعْدَهُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَعَاوِدْ بِلَفْظٍ وَاسْأَلْ اللُّطْفَ وَاجْهَدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيَس إِنْ تُتْلَى يُخَفَّفُ مَوْتُهُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَيُرْفَعُ عَنْهُ الإِصْرَ عِنْدَ التَّلَحَّدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَوَجِّهْهُ عِنْدَ الْمَوْتِ تِلْقَاءَ قِبْلَةٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَإِنْ مَاتَ غَمِّضْهُ وَلَحْيَيْهِ فَاشْدُدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَمَلْبُوسَهُ فَاخْلَعْ وَلَيِّنْ مَفَاصِلاً<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَضَعْ فَوْقَ بَطْنِ الْمَيِّتِ مَانِعَ مُصْعِدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَوَفِّ دُيُونَ الْمَيِّتِ شَرْعًا وَفَرِّقَنْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَصِيَّةَ عَدْلٍ ثُمَّ تَجْهِيزَهُ أُقْصُدِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>